{"title":"Linux常用操作","date":"2019-09-26T09:15:33.000Z","link":"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作","tags":["Linux","笔记"],"updated":"2019-11-02T06:56:14.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"基础操作\">基础操作<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#基础操作\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"关闭系统\">关闭系统<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#关闭系统\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#halt</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#shutdown -h 10 #10分钟后关闭</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#poweroff</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"重启系统\">重启系统<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#重启系统\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#shutdown -r 10 #10分钟后重启系统 取消重启使用命令shutdown -c</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#reboot</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#init 6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"目录与文件\">目录与文件<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#目录与文件\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#pwd #查看当前完整目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cd #返回/root根路径</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cd..#返回上一级目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cd /root/usr #进入/root/usr目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#mkdir temp #在当前路径创建temp文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"修改tab键缩进空格长度\">修改tab键缩进空格长度<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#修改tab键缩进空格长度\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#vi ~/.vimrc #编辑这个文件，有可能为空</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\">在vimrc添加一行代码 -- <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> tabstop=4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\">wq保存</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"head与tail命令\">head与tail命令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#head与tail命令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#head -10 file#显示文件前10行</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#tail -10 file#显示文件后10行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"cat命令\">cat命令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#cat命令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cat &gt; file#创建一个文件，并且开始写入Ctrl+D结束编辑</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cat file#显示文件文本内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"uniq命令\">uniq命令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#uniq命令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#uniq file#显示去除重复行后的文件内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"grep命令\">grep命令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#grep命令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#grep 'a' file#显示包含字母a的行</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#grep -c 'a' file#显示包含字母a的行的行数</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#head -10 file#显示文件前10行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"复制文件-更改文件名字\">复制文件 更改文件名字<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#复制文件-更改文件名字\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#mv a b #将文件名a改为文件名b</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#mv a root/#移动文件到root目录下</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cp a root/ #复制文件到root目录下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"find-whereis-which-查找命令\">find whereis which 查找命令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#find-whereis-which-查找命令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#find -name \"java*\" #查找java开头的文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#find -atime -1 #搜索一天内存取过的文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#find / -empty #查找空目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#find / -user nice #查找属于nice的文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#whereis python #查看python的位置,whereis只能查找源代码，二进制文件，帮助文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#which python #查看python的位置，只能查找$PATH环境变量中的文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"压缩解压\">压缩解压<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#压缩解压\"></a></h4><h4 id=\"进程操作\">进程操作<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#进程操作\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#ps -A #查看当前所有进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#ps -ef | grep java #查看名为java的进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#pkill java #终止程序名为java的进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#killall -9 java #终止程序名为java的进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#kill -9 1024 #终止进程号为1024的进程</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"显示历史指令\">显示历史指令<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#显示历史指令\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#history 100 #显示输入的最近100条历史指令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"实用操作\">实用操作<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#实用操作\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"安装Python3-7\">安装Python3.7<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#安装Python3-7\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#yum -y install gcc #安装依赖</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#yum -y install zlib-devel bzip2-devel openssl-devel ncurses-devel sqlite-devel readline-devel tk-devel gdbm-devel db4-devel libpcap-devel xz-devel libffi-devel #安装其他依赖包</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.0/Python-3.7.0.tgz #下载python3.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#tar -zxvf Python-3.7.0.tgz #解压</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#mkdir /usr/local/python3 #建立存放python3.7的目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#cd Python-3.7.0 #进入解压后的目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#./configure --prefix=/usr/local/python3 #安装到/usr/local/python3</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#make &amp;&amp; make install #安装命令</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#ln -s /usr/local/python3/bin/python3.7 /usr/bin/python3 #建立软链接</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#ln -s /usr/local/python3/bin/pip3.7 /usr/bin/pip3 #建立软链接</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#python3 #python3.7命令</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root~]#pip3 #pip3命令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"vi编辑器\">vi编辑器<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#vi编辑器\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root~]#set number显示行号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"后台永久运行jar\">后台永久运行jar<a href=\"2019/09/26/Linux常用操作#后台永久运行jar\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nohup java -jar blog-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar &gt; log.file 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>log.file为日志输出文件</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Python利用ip代理和多线程批量爬取中国联通手机欠费金额","link":"2019/09/26/Python利用ip代理和多线程批量爬取中国联通手机欠费金额"},"next":{"title":"centOS安装操作Docker","link":"2019/09/21/centOS安装操作Docker"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/09/26/Linux常用操作/"}